"cc_Greenhouse.John":"I've always wanted a greenhouse of my own one day.#$b#I love plants.$1",
"cc_Minecart.John":"The minecarts were fixed last night.#$b#If you use them be careful of roaming animals.$3",
"joja_Begin.John":"So, I heard Joja is taking over the community construction project…#$b#Guess we don't need a community center after all.$3",
"movieTheater.John":"Finally, something interesting is happening today!#$b#Just heard there's a new movie theater in Pelican town!$1",
"dumped_Guys.John":"There's such a thing as a healthy polyamorous romance.$2#$b#You shouldn't have lied.$3",
"secondChance_Guys.John":"I really wouldn't do that again, @.$3",
"dumped_Girls.John":"You're impossible.#$b#Why would you hurt so many people?$5",
"secondChance_Girls.John":"I'm surprised you're getting a second chance.$3",
"pamHouseUpgrade.John":"Helping Pam like that, it was really kind of you.$1",
"pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous.John":"It's amazing how full of love people are.#$b#Now, Pam finally has a good home to live in.$1",
"WipedMemory.John": "Oh hello, I'm John.$1#$b#...#$b#...$2#$b#Wait, do I know you?$3",
"JohnsBadSide.John": "After a long hour of convincing, I talked Pop into staying at the temple. Someone needs to look out for him, since you obviously don't want to.$5",
"JohnsGoodSide.John": "I actually talked Pop into moving into the temple, I'm planning on building a extra room too just for him.$1",
"JohnsArrival.John": "I'm finally completely unpacked and Noodles is adjusting really well to her new home too.$1#$b#Maybe this move is a good thing.$1",
"FaintingIncident.John": "I'm okay, I took Harvey's advice and made an appointment too, that fainting incident was just too much.$2",
"HaleysGossip.John": "Haley approached me, she actually apologized...Maybe she's not so bad after all.$1",
"WildHog.John": "I spoke to Marnie and it turns out I was right, some of her hogs did escape...So be careful okay?$2",
"TheIllness.John": "I know I should be upset about the chronic illness diagnoses, but for some reason I'm just happy I know what's wrong with me finally.$1",
"TheTemple.John": "I've a pretty good amount of savings, fixing up this Temple will be easy in that regard.$1",
"JohnsDesperation.John": "I feel so embarrassed, I can't believe that even magic can't cure me.$1#$b#But...At least I have a way to help the pain.$3",
"JohnsDisappointment.John": "I'm sorry for yelling at you the other night, I really thought magic could do anything.$3#$b#I didn't even consider it could hurt me.$2",
"HouseParty.John": "Having Roger at the party, it was actually really nice. I didn't realize how much I missed him.",
"VillainInTheValley.John": "Pop is such a weird little character, he doesn't realize it but I've been leaving Seaglass near his nest, that way he can collect them too.$1",
"ChasePopOff.John": "Pop told me you tried to steal his trash?$3#$b#You should leave him alone @, he's grown on me.$3",
"EncouragePop.John": "Pop wants to be the best villain in the valley, but I'm hoping to get him the side of good. He's too adorable to be so evil.$1",
"BarronsGoodSide.John": "It was so nice having a hot meal together and Pop was so happy.$1#$b#I want to see him smile more often.$1",
"BarronsBadSide.John": "Oh hey, you know trying to deny Pop something to eat, that was real low of you.$3#$b#You can do better that crap.$5",
"BusFire.John": "Barron told me she caught her stove on fire, poor thing looked so embarrassed by it.$2",
"FindingPhoebe.John": "I couldn't imagine a life where I would ever give my child up...I hope this woman is what Barron needs and not someone that will cause her problems.$3",
"PhoebeArrives.John": "Barron's Biological mother is so...Odd...but I do like her.$1",
"JinxIllness.John": "Jinx has been acting so strange, like she's getting ready for something important.$3",
