"sat.Popper.winter": "%He's hiding something.#$e#What?#$b#What are you a cop?#$b#I'm not up to anything...",
"sun.Popper.winter": "You!#$b#Take this and run! Don't let anyone take!$5[Fellowclown.AND_Button]",
